flowchart TD
 U[ADMIN / DOCTOR / PATIENT] --> C[Prescription Servlet]
 C --> S[PrescriptionService]
 S --> O{Ownership allowed?}
 O -- No --> D[Access denied + audit]
 O -- Yes --> M[MedicalRecordDao]
 M --> Q{Prescription exists?}
 Q -- Yes --> B[Duplicate block]
 Q -- No --> T[Create transaction]
 T --> H[PrescriptionDao header]
 H --> I[PrescriptionItemDao items]
 I --> DB[(Oracle XE)]
 S --> E[Edit: update header + delete/replace items]
 S --> ST[ACTIVE to COMPLETED/CANCELLED]
 S --> P[Patient read-only / print flow]
